description: Great Lakes Graphite Inc., doing business as NovoCarbon Corporation, operates as a clean technology minerals processing company that supplies carbon products. It offers high purity graphite products, spherical graphite products, and micronized graphite products. The company was formerly known as Shield Gold Inc. and changed its name to Great Lakes Graphite Inc. in May 2014. Great Lakes Graphite Inc. is based in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. James A. Richardson B.A, C.A., CPA, FIPA
